Package org.anchoranalysis.plugin.quick.bean.structure

Class ExperimentResultsExperimentStructure

Object
AnchorBean<FilesProvider>
FilesProvider
ExperimentResultsExperimentStructure
public class ExperimentResultsExperimentStructure
extends FilesProvider
Finds some files produced in a previous experiment assuming a certain structure

A convenience method for commonly used prefixer settings when the output occurs in an experiment/$1/ filesystem structure where $1 is the experimentType
